# RETRY VERIFICATION (Attempt {{.AttemptNum}})

This is a re-verification after a previous attempt failed. The previous
verification report is at `{{.WfDir}}/verify.attempt-{{.AttemptNum}}.md`.

When verifying:
1. Check whether each issue from the previous report has been resolved
2. For each previously flagged issue, confirm the fix is correct
3. Note any issues that remain unfixed
4. Check whether the fixes introduced any new problems
5. If all previous issues are resolved and no new issues exist, **PASS**
